fields.physical_description:
1. box lid, card printed in colours to show the title, details and photographs of characters and X-wing fighter
2. box base, white card 
3. box lining, white card 
4. box compartment, white card
5. box compartment, card covered with black paper 
6. board game, card with the outside covered with paper printed with white dots on black and in blue and white to show the name Star Wars and its symbol of two figures. The playing surface is covered with paper printed in colours to black to show both illustrations and photographs from the Star Wars theme. Moves are made on a radiating pattern of circles. The board folds in half. 
7. spinner, card printed in colours on black to winning/losing scores 1 to 
    3, with a red plastic arrow shape spinner 
8-16. sheet of playing tokens, card printed in colours to show 8 tokens; 2 each in red, blue, green and yellow   *These are still attached to each other. 
17-24. round bases for playing tokens, black plastic. *These are still sealed in their plastic bag. 
25-28. Death Star Blueprint Cards 
29-32. Tractor Beam Cards 
33-83. Force Cards, 51 instructional cards (there should be 52 cards) 84. instructions sheet
85. protective lining sheet to stop the playing surface rubbing when stored
fields.title: Escape From Death Star
